   ad:'Hyperkalaemia (cardiac protection): 10ml 10% IV over 2-3 min (repeat once if ECG unchanged). Symptomatic hypocalcaemia: 10-20ml 10% in 50-100ml glucose 5% over 15-30 min.',af:'Slow IV bolus or infusion',ar:'IV',am:'Per clinical need and Ca level',
