   pd:'Not established <18y for smoking cessation',pm:0,pf:'BD',pr:'Oral',pw:'Noradrenaline-dopamine reuptake inhibitor (NDRI). UK: licensed for smoking cessation only (not depression). US: antidepressant (Wellbutrin). Lowers seizure threshold — CONTRAINDICATED in eating disorders (bulimia/anorexia), seizure disorder, alcohol/benzodiazepine withdrawal. Insomnia (take in morning — not evening). No sexual dysfunction. No weight gain. CYP2B6 and CYP2D6 — interactions (SSRIs, antipsychotics). Dry mouth. Agitation.',
