   ci:['TPMT deficiency (homozygous — contraindicated)','Allopurinol concurrent (unless dose reduced 25%)','Hypersensitivity','Active serious infection'],ca:['TPMT genotyping/phenotyping before starting','Allopurinol interaction (CRITICAL — dose reduction 25%)','FBC (weekly x4 weeks; then monthly x3; then 3-monthly — myelosuppression)','LFTs (monthly)','Pancreatitis (stop if occurs)','Lymphoma risk (long-term)'],
