   pd:'Not established.',pm:0,pf:'Once weekly (SC); once daily (oral)',pr:'SC/oral',pw:'Long-acting GLP-1 receptor agonist (once weekly). T2DM (Ozempic — SUSTAIN, SOUL trials — CV benefit). Obesity (Wegovy — STEP trials — average 15-17% body weight loss — landmark weight loss results). Oral formulation (Rybelsus — lower bioavailability — must be taken fasting 30 min before food). SURMOUNT-4 (weight regain on stopping — lifelong treatment implied). Nausea (dose-dependent). Pancreatitis. Aspiration risk (gastroparesis — anaesthesia consideration — withhold before GA). Thyroid C-cell (same MEN2 concern as liraglutide). GLP-1 shortage (supply issues 2022-2025).',
